## Claude Hooks Integration

Configure hooks in `.claude/settings.json` for automation:

**Example: Auto-format on edit**
```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "command": "prettier --write \"$FILE_PATH\""
    }]
  }
}
```

