## GitHub Integration

Claude can interact with GitHub via `gh` CLI:

```bash
# Issues
gh issue list
gh issue view 123
gh issue create --title "..." --body "..."

# PRs
gh pr list
gh pr view 123
gh pr create --title "..." --body "..."

# Project boards
gh project list --owner your-org
```

**Automatic:** Claude checks issues at session start if `/start-session` enabled.

